"Ubambe izinkinobho zombili yasemuva neyaphansi imizuzwana emithathu ukuze usebenzise i-%1$s.

 Ukuze unike amandla i-%1$s manje, phinda ubambe inkinobho yasemuva neyaphansi imizuzwana emithathu. Sebenzisa lesi sinqamuleli noma nini ukuze unike amandla noma ukhubaze i-%1$s.

 Ungalungisa okuncamelayo Kumasethingi > Isistimu > Ukufinyeleleka."

"Uma kuvulwe isinqamuleli, ukucindezela zombili izinkinobho ezingemuva neziphansi ngamasekhondi ama-3 kuzoqalisa isici sokufinyelela.

 Isici samanje sokufinyelela:
 %1$s

 Ungashintsha isici Kumasethingi > Ukufinyeleleka."
